candidateOnboarding.title: Candidate Application
candidateOnboarding.intro: Welcome to your desktop. This application will help you manage your profile on an ongoing basic. You can update your resume and apply to a new job using your existing resume with out re-enting the same.
candidateOnboarding.content: Updating your resume on regular basic will help you find a job faster. You will get the stsatus of your application on-line. You can also confirm/reschedule your interview and give us feedback on the hiring process. A section on "getting started" has been included to enable you to understand the system better. Do contact us through the helpdesk, if you have any clarifications.
